He's got a red shirt.

111
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:18,603
Okay, let's go.

112
00:13:20,570 --> 00:13:23,289
Freeze! Give me the gun! Up, up!

113
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,842
How's it feel, sucker?

114
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:27,326
Shoot him!

115
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:28,486
Drop it!

116
00:13:28,770 --> 00:13:30,328
Shoot him! Shoot him!

117
00:13:30,690 --> 00:13:32,999
-Shut the fuck up!
-Shoot this prick!

118
00:13:34,170 --> 00:13:36,559
Shoot him! Somebody shoot this prick!

119
00:13:36,890 --> 00:13:38,164
Shoot me.

120
00:13:38,490 --> 00:13:40,640
Shut up! Put them down!

121
00:13:41,010 --> 00:13:43,922
-I warn you! I'm going to shoot you!
-Shoot him!

122
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:45,888
Shut the fuck up! Shut up!

123
00:13:46,130 --> 00:13:48,166
Shoot me! Shoot him!

124
00:13:55,410 --> 00:13:56,729
Get him out of there.

125
00:13:58,170 --> 00:13:59,603
It ain't worth it.

126
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:09,409
Hey, wait up already!

127
00:16:31,810 --> 00:16:33,402
Merry Christmas!

128
00:17:00,530 --> 00:17:02,248
I miss you...

129
00:17:04,810 --> 00:17:06,402
...Victoria Lynn.

130
00:17:19,810 --> 00:17:21,721
That's silly, isn't it?

131
00:17:27,290 --> 00:17:29,008
I'll see you later.

132
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:32,601
I'll see you much later.

133
00:17:38,490 --> 00:17:41,050
