Psychos "R" Us?

232
00:23:10,970 --> 00:23:12,289
I don't think you're funny.

233
00:23:12,530 --> 00:23:15,124
I don't think this whole
goddamn setup is funny.

234
00:23:15,410 --> 00:23:17,970
