Tell me I'm wrong!

235
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:19,485
You're not wrong.

236
00:23:19,890 --> 00:23:22,085
And you expect me to trust these bozos?

237
00:23:22,330 --> 00:23:24,525
My people are loyal to me.

238
00:23:24,850 --> 00:23:26,283
Bullshit.

239
00:23:26,650 --> 00:23:27,719
Do you smoke?

240
00:23:27,970 --> 00:23:29,881
