250
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:54,004
Mr. Joshua, your left arm, please.

251
00:24:02,450 --> 00:24:06,443
Hey, you guys are fucking gone.
You know what I am saying?

252
00:24:06,770 --> 00:24:08,681
Jesus Christ, man!

253
00:24:09,650 --> 00:24:12,847
You guys are fucking crazy, man. Come on!

254
00:24:17,410 --> 00:24:19,446
Have Endo look at that, Mr. Joshua.

255
