Want to tell me about it?

770
01:01:26,810 --> 01:01:29,085
-About what?
-Don't bullshit me.

771
01:01:29,330 --> 01:01:32,606
Your daughter wasn't killed
for something she was into.

772
01:01:32,850 --> 01:01:34,966
She was killed for something you're into.

773
01:01:36,650 --> 01:01:37,799
Stop me if I'm wrong.

774
01:01:39,090 --> 01:01:41,046
