775
01:01:42,170 --> 01:01:45,003
Keep your hands away from your pocket, okay?

776
01:01:45,610 --> 01:01:46,406
Easy, man.

777
01:01:46,610 --> 01:01:47,406
Fuck easy.

778
01:01:50,330 --> 01:01:53,606
You called me the other day
to blow the whistle, right?

779
01:01:54,290 --> 01:01:55,803
Blow the whistle on what?

780
01:01:56,010 --> 01:01:59,161
