your little girl.

784
01:02:07,850 --> 01:02:09,806
Chrissake!
I've got another daughter.

785
01:02:10,050 --> 01:02:13,201
-She'll be protected.
-You don't know these people.

786
01:02:13,690 --> 01:02:15,408
