the whole thing down.

793
01:02:44,050 --> 01:02:45,802
We killed everybody.

794
01:02:50,650 --> 01:02:52,322
We also formed a plan.

795
01:02:52,730 --> 01:02:53,799
Keep talking.

796
01:02:59,770 --> 01:03:03,001
A few years ago, Shadow Company
got together again.

797
01:03:03,410 --> 01:03:05,002
