894
01:11:51,370 --> 01:11:55,124
We do this my way.
You shoot and you shoot to kill.

895
01:11:55,610 --> 01:11:59,888
Get as many as you can.
All you got to do is just not miss.

896
01:12:00,090 --> 01:12:01,569
