900
01:12:18,810 --> 01:12:20,607
You're gonna have to trust me.

901
01:12:24,450 --> 01:12:25,724
Here we go.

902
01:12:32,170 --> 01:12:36,243
We don 't want your daughter.
We want to know what Hunsaker told you.

903
01:12:36,450 --> 01:12:40,329
Dry lake. Victorville.
Sunrise tomorrow. Be there.

904
01:15:37,610 --> 01:15:38,884
Murtaugh!

905
01:15:39,490 --> 01:15:40,843
Yes, that's right.

906
01:15:41,090 --> 01:15:42,967
Show me my daughter!

907
01:15:43,290 --> 01:15:46,009
Let me see her, then I'll come quietly.

908
01:15:52,690 --> 01:15:54,282
He wants to see the girl.

909
01:15:54,490 --> 01:15:55,684
Get out.

910
01:16:00,970 --> 01:16:02,164
Daddy!

911
01:16:02,650 --> 01:16:04,880
Okay, baby! I'm here.

912
01:16:05,370 --> 01:16:07,201
Okay, it's all right.

913
01:16:07,450 --> 01:16:08,360
Simple exchange.

914
01:16:09,370 --> 01:16:12,806
You come with us,
the girl takes a walk.

915
01:16:13,050 --> 01:16:14,449
Let her go now.

916
01:16:16,610 --> 01:16:20,046
As I say, take your hands
out of your pockets.

917
01:16:20,250 --> 01:16:21,842
Sure thing, pal.

918
01:16:25,530 --> 01:16:26,485
It's alive.

919
01:16:28,890 --> 01:16:31,404
Let her go now, or we all die.

920
01:16:32,210 --> 01:16:33,245
Take him!

921
01:16:33,570 --> 01:16:34,764
He has a grenade!

922
01:16:35,010 --> 01:16:37,843
He's bluffing!
He wouldn't risk killing his daughter.

923
01:16:38,610 --> 01:16:40,089
If she's gonna die...

924
01:16:40,330 --> 01:16:43,606
. . .she's gonna die with me.
My way, not yours.

925
01:16:48,570 --> 01:16:52,768
Come on, Roger, get out of the way.
Move to your left. Come on!

926
01:16:53,010 --> 01:16:54,409
Put the pin back in.

927
01:16:54,890 --> 01:16:58,565
Officer Murtaugh, don't be foolish.
Look at the hardware.

928
01:16:58,890 --> 01:17:00,448
Move to your left.

929
01:17:05,890 --> 01:17:09,246
Look at the firepower.
You're grounded. Riggs is gone.

930
01:17:09,610 --> 01:17:11,680
Put the pin back in the grenade.

931
01:17:11,890 --> 01:17:13,403
If you come closer...

932
01:17:13,890 --> 01:17:15,118
...then we all die.

933
01:17:16,610 --> 01:17:18,202
I don't think so.

934
01:17:25,890 --> 01:17:27,608
Come on, honey.

935
01:17:29,610 --> 01:17:30,565
Just a smoker.

936
01:17:30,810 --> 01:17:31,606
Bingo.

937
01:17:36,930 --> 01:17:37,760
Where is he?

938
01:17:37,970 --> 01:17:38,766
It's Riggs.

939
01:17:41,090 --> 01:17:43,320
Rianne, get in the car!

940
01:17:44,930 --> 01:17:46,568
Get in the fucking car!

941
01:18:03,810 --> 01:18:05,243
Go, Rianne, go!

942
01:18:05,570 --> 01:18:08,209
Come on, cottontail, stick your head up.

943
01:18:09,610 --> 01:18:11,999
That's it, you son of a bitch.
Good night.

944
01:18:15,530 --> 01:18:18,124
Don't try it, son.
You're not that fast.

945
01:18:20,050 --> 01:18:21,802
Hello, Joshua. Hello, Joshua.

946
01:18:22,010 --> 01:18:23,682
-Yes, sir.
-I got Riggs.

947
01:18:24,450 --> 01:18:27,044
He's got Riggs. Go get the girl!

948
01:19:01,010 --> 01:19:02,921
Throw your weapon down!

949
01:19:03,170 --> 01:19:05,400
Put your hands behind your head!

950
01:19:09,330 --> 01:19:12,845
You're Gen. Peter McAllister,
commander of Shadow Company.

951
01:19:13,250 --> 01:19:15,810
I see we've heard of each other.

952
01:19:16,010 --> 01:19:19,400
Yep. It'll almost be a shame
when I nail you.

953
01:19:20,290 --> 01:19:24,442
I ran into some of those Shadow Company
pussies in Saigon in '69.

954
01:19:24,730 --> 01:19:25,958
You did, did you?

955
01:20:11,170 --> 01:20:12,922
Leave me alone!

956
01:20:38,570 --> 01:20:40,765
Save your strength.
You'll need it.

957
01:20:41,170 --> 01:20:42,080
Who's the Chin?

958
01:20:43,250 --> 01:20:45,718
Endo, meet Mr. Martin Riggs.

959
01:20:46,810 --> 01:20:49,643
