about dispensing pain...

960
01:20:49,850 --> 01:20:51,044
...than we'll ever know.

961
01:20:52,850 --> 01:20:54,522
See, we have a problem.

962
01:20:54,730 --> 01:20:56,448
Since we have Murtaugh...

963
01:20:56,970 --> 01:20:58,198
...we don't need you.

964
01:20:58,530 --> 01:21:01,761
-I believe in being thorough.
-I've heard that about you.

965
01:21:03,890 --> 01:21:06,450
Our problem, and yours too...

966
01:21:07,170 --> 01:21:10,048
...is we have a shipment
of merchandise to deliver.

967
01:21:10,250 --> 01:21:12,047
Why don't you just call it heroin?

968
01:21:13,650 --> 01:21:15,925
