969
01:21:16,850 --> 01:21:18,681
It would be unfortunate...

970
01:21:18,890 --> 01:21:21,529
...if we showed up
to deliver our heroin...

971
01:21:22,170 --> 01:21:23,842
...and were surrounded by 50 cops.

972
01:21:24,050 --> 01:21:25,199
That would be too bad.

973
01:21:25,450 --> 01:21:26,929
Yes, it would be.

974
01:21:27,850 --> 01:21:30,648
So we have to find out all the cops know.

975
01:21:30,850 --> 01:21:33,683
We don't know shit.
You did Hunsaker before he could say...

976
01:21:35,970 --> 01:21:39,360
I wish I could believe you.
Unfortunately, I don't.

977
01:21:44,290 --> 01:21:47,043
