983
01:22:09,570 --> 01:22:12,528
We're in for a long night,
because I don't know shit.

984
01:22:14,770 --> 01:22:16,089
We'll see.

985
01:22:24,490 --> 01:22:25,366
Hit him again!

986
01:22:35,090 --> 01:22:35,886
Again!

987
01:22:41,090 --> 01:22:42,569
Tell me about the shipment!

988
01:22:44,890 --> 01:22:47,324
I'm gonna fucking kill both of you!

989
01:22:47,570 --> 01:22:49,845
Very funny.
What about the shipment?

990
01:22:55,290 --> 01:22:57,281
The shipment, Mr. Murtaugh.

991
01:22:57,730 --> 01:22:59,482
Go spit!

992
01:23:00,770 --> 01:23:01,646
