Nobody can take that.

998
01:23:35,770 --> 01:23:37,044
Fine.

999
01:23:37,250 --> 01:23:38,603
Badass soldier, huh?

1000
01:23:52,650 --> 01:23:53,765
Get her up.

1001
01:23:58,690 --> 01:24:01,250
Untie me and I'll kill all of you bastards!

1002
01:24:01,450 --> 01:24:03,122
Tell me what you know.

1003
01:24:03,330 --> 01:24:05,924
Fuck you, bastard!
I'll kill you!

1004
01:24:13,090 --> 01:24:14,808
Sorry, pal.
Say good night.

1005
01:24:35,770 --> 01:24:38,887
That's a real good-looking young woman...

1006
01:24:39,090 --> 01:24:41,365
...you got there, Mr. Murtaugh.

1007
01:24:44,170 --> 01:24:45,319
I've told you everything.

1008
01:24:45,530 --> 01:24:46,963
We'll soon know, won't we?

1009
01:24:47,170 --> 01:24:48,683
I'm warning you.

1010
01:24:49,130 --> 01:24:49,926
Don't.

1011
01:24:50,370 --> 01:24:52,486
Spare me, son. It's over.

1012
01:24:52,970 --> 01:24:55,325
There's no more heroes left in the world.

1013
01:25:00,570 --> 01:25:01,764
Kill that son of a bitch!

1014
01:25:12,770 --> 01:25:14,362
That asshole's getting away!

1015
01:25:14,610 --> 01:25:16,521
Who's fucking next?

1016
01:25:16,970 --> 01:25:18,449
McAllister!

1017
01:25:18,690 --> 01:25:19,805
Who's next?

1018
01:25:22,770 --> 01:25:24,283
Pretty thin, huh?

1019
01:25:24,530 --> 01:25:25,929
Anorexic.

1020
01:25:33,130 --> 01:25:35,325
